   "Whenever I see my past I realize two things in it. One is your pleasant smile and other is your support with me all the time. One thing I really didn’t understand you were conscious about me to take decision whether you love me or not. I think you were really not aware of want your heart says. That’s why it was got pretty late to get the decision from your side.",
